## Directory Check
- "dir": Show root directory of the project and files:
  ```
  DEBUG: Project Root Directory Info
  - Files in root:
    [LIST ALL FILES IN ROOT]
  ```

## Core Commands
- "system check": Report file status:
  ```
  DEBUG: File Status
  - Core files status:
    - @README.md
    - @DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md
    - @DEVELOPMENT_STATUS.md
  ```